long-description.p:
A quick cache and dash but some discretion will be required as the store is very busy.
Cache is a magnetic in a public location and contains only a log.The area is Not entirely wheelchair-friendly as some reaching is required.
There is no access to this cache from the sliproad of the M50 so don't be tempted to try it.
Please take care and rehide the cache to prevent muggles from discovering its location.
